                            <comment id="13737562" author="hossman" created="Mon, 12 Aug 2013 23:50:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i&apos;ve pinned the test to use LogDocMergePolicy, and am going to assume this has &quot;fixed&quot; things until/unless we see some new failures.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
